nt child abuse and neglect at covered programs consistent with the standards specified by this Act.</p> <p>(Sec. 8) Directs the Secretary of Health and Human Services to study and report to Congress on outcomes for children in both private and public covered programs under this Act encompassing a broad representation of treatment facilities and geographic regions.</p> <p><br> </p>]]></text>
